===subject:Genetic testing and cloning
===message:For the first situation in which an individual has the option of finding out whether or not they have Hunington's disease, if I were the person in this situation...I think I would get the genetic test done.  I would want to know whether or not my health is at risk and I would want to prepare my self and my family for the future.

For the cloning situations, I don't think any of those situations are justified for cloning.  I personally believe that things happen for a reason...and God would not have taken away anything that wasn't meant to be.  Plus, cloning goes against the natural selection process.  Every thing must be little different in order for natural selection to presist.
=========yorg=========
